[FILE:274:descriptions/desc.primary]
QtKeychain is a Qt API to store passwords and other secret data securely.

For Linux/Unix, GNOME Keyring is used to store the data, otherwise
QtKeychain tries to use KWallet (via D-Bus), if available.
Libsecret (common API for desktop-specific solutions) is also supported.


